sub_title: Analytics Consultant | ORTEC - Optimize Your World
summary: One of my passions is mathematics; the infinite applications of math fasinates me. Therefore, I get a lot energy from applying my mathematical knowledge and analytic reasoning to optimize business processes. I am reliable, eager to learn and hands-on. My work attitude can be described as motivated and persistent.
